PREREQUISITES
bashhate		(optionnal) automated style checker for bash scripts
bc				arbitrary precision numeric processing language
csvtool			to manipulate CSV files
curl			to upload to FTP server
ffmpeg			for video conversion and drawing text overlays
FitCSVTool.jar	Java archive provided as part of Garmin Fit SDK
				it can be downloaded here https://developer.garmin.com/fit/download/
java			jre version 1.8.0 or higher, to run the file FitCSVTool.jar
jq				lightweight and flexible command-line JSON processor
				used for parsing ffmpeg json outputs
shellcheck 		(optionnal) analysis tool that automatically finds bugs in your shell scripts

HOW TO VERIFY CODE
bashate *.sh \
&& shellcheck --check-sourced --external-sources main.sh \
&& bash -o noexec main.sh

HOW TO RUN
./main.sh
